Trade/Device Name(s): WaveSense KeyNote Codeless Blood Glucose Monitoring System
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): WaveSense KeyNote Codeless Blood Glucose Meter
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for the AgaMatrix WaveSense KeyNote Codeless Blood Glucose Monitoring System intended for quantitative measurement of glucose in capillary whole blood.
Indications for Use Summary: For quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from finger, palm, or forearm; for home use by persons with diabetes or in clinical settings as an aid to monitor diabetes control.
